headline: RBC upgrades CSX, says shares gain under most rail merger outcomes
summary: Investing.com -- RBC upgraded CSX Corp to Outperform, saying the railroad is positioned to benefit under nearly any outcome from the proposed Union Pacific–Norfolk Southern merger. The brokerage also raised its price target on stock to $39 from $37.

headline: CSX Corp. Announces Date for Third Quarter Earnings Release and Earnings Call
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Sept. 18, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX Corp. (NASDAQ: CSX) will release third quarter financial and operating results after the market close on Thursday, October 16, 2025. This will be followed by a conference call and live webcast hosted by the company’s management team at 4:30 p.m. Eastern Time.
